<div style="text-align: center; color: black;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.8em;">Invitation</h1>
    <p>You have been invited by <%= sender %> to collaborate in MaaS.</p>
    <p>Please click on the link below to become <%= role %> of the company: <%= company %></p>
    <div style="padding: 2em;">
        <a href="<%= inviteHref %>" style="margin: 1em;
                                        padding: 1em 2em;
                                        background-color: #333;
                                        border-radius: 0.5em;
                                        -webkit-box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px 0px #d3d3d3;
                                        -moz-box-shadow:    2px 2px 5px 0px #d3d3d3;
                                        box-shadow:         2px 2px 5px 0px #d3d3d3;
                                        color: #90EE90;
                                        text-decoration: none;
                                        font-weight: bold">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p><%= inviteHref %></p>
    <p>If you don't want to accept the invitation just ignore this email.</p>
    <p>MaaS team</p>
</div>